OL,3,CNHS facing 'huge holes' in workforce
OL,4,Cif foreign doctors leave UK, report
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FThe NHS could be left with "huge
OL,8,Fholes" in its medical workforce if
OL,9,Fforeign doctors leave the health
OL,10,Fservice, according to the medical
OL,11,Fregulator.
OL,13,FA new General Medical Council (GMC)
OL,14,Freport has revealed that 4,880 doctors
OL,15,Fwho trained abroad left the UK
OL,16,Fworkforce in 2024 ` a 26% increase on
OL,17,F3,869 in 2023.
OL,19,FDoctors who qualified outside of the
OL,20,FUK currently make up around 42% of the
OL,21,Fworkforce, it said.
