OL,3,CNHS facing 'huge holes' in workforce
OL,4,Cif foreign doctors leave UK, report
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FGMC chief executive Charlie Massey
OL,8,Fsaid: "Doctors represent a mobile
OL,9,Fworkforce, whose skills are in high
OL,10,Fdemand around the world.
OL,11,FInternationally qualified doctors who
OL,12,Fhave historically chosen to work in
OL,13,Fthe UK could quite conceivably choose
OL,14,Fto leave if they feel they have no
OL,15,Ffuture job progression here, or if the
OL,16,Fcountry feels less welcoming.
