OL,3,CNHS facing 'huge holes' in workforce
OL,4,Cif foreign doctors leave UK, report
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"Any hardening of rhetoric and falling
OL,8,Faway of support could undermine the
OL,9,FUK's image as somewhere the brightest
OL,10,Fand the best from all over the world
OL,11,Fwant to work.
OL,13,F"It is vital that workforce policies
OL,14,Fdo not inadvertently demoralise or
OL,15,Fdrive out the talent on which our
OL,16,Fhealth services depend.
OL,18,F"Doctors who qualified outside of the
OL,19,FUK make up 42% of those working in the
OL,20,FUK.
