OL,3,CNHS facing 'huge holes' in workforce
OL,4,Cif foreign doctors leave UK, report
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"If we see even a small percentage
OL,8,Fincrease in them leaving, our health
OL,9,Fservices will end up with huge holes
OL,10,Fthat they'll struggle to fill."
OL,12,FIt comes after health leaders warned
OL,13,Fthat St George's flags are creating
OL,14,F"no-go zones" for NHS staff, with some
OL,15,Ffacing frequent abuse.
