OL,3,CNHS facing 'huge holes' in workforce
OL,4,Cif foreign doctors leave UK, report
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FWorkers feel intimidated by the
OL,8,Fpresence of the flags across the
OL,9,Fcountry, including when they are
OL,10,Fvisiting people in their own homes to
OL,11,Fgive them treatment, according to
OL,12,Fseveral NHS trust chief executives and
OL,13,Fleaders.
OL,15,FAn NHS Providers poll of senior
OL,16,Fmanagers found 45% were extremely
OL,17,Fconcerned about discrimination towards
OL,18,FNHS staff from patients and the
OL,19,Fpublic, while a further 33% were
OL,20,Fmoderately concerned.
