OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FMr Massey added: "Whatever the future
OL,8,Fmakeup of the workforce, we all ` from
OL,9,Femployers to regulators, policymakers
OL,10,Fto the profession itself ` have a duty
OL,11,Fto recognise the essential
OL,12,Fcontribution all doctors make,
OL,13,Firrespective of background, and to
OL,14,Fensure that each one is supported and
OL,15,Fvalued accordingly."
