OL,4,Cif foreign doctors leave UK, report
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FSpeaking last week about resident
OL,8,Fdoctors going on strike, Health
OL,9,FSecretary Wes Streeting said he was
OL,10,Fproposing changes to improve doctors'
OL,11,Flives, including more training places
OL,12,Fand changes to international
OL,13,Frecruitment.
OL,15,FHe acknowledged that two-thirds of the
OL,16,F30,000 doctors applying for 10,000
OL,17,Ftraining places are international
OL,18,Fmedical graduates.
