OL,3,CNHS facing 'huge holes' in workforce
OL,4,Cif foreign doctors leave UK, report
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FMr Streeting said: "One of the things
OL,8,Fthat I'm doing is putting an end to
OL,9,Fthe absurdity where homegrown talent
OL,10,Fare having to compete for the same
OL,11,Ftraining places on equal terms against
OL,12,Fpeople who've trained overseas.
OL,14,F"I think it's crackers. I think it's
OL,15,Funfair to our own doctors. I also
OL,16,Fthink it doesn't help this country
OL,17,Fwith unmanageable levels of net
OL,18,Fmigration.
